OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMinimum staff levels       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdemanded in school strikes 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Schools and colleges in England will be
OL,6, asked to make sure a minimum number of 
OL,7, staff are working on any future strike 
OL,8, dates, the government has announced.   
OL,10,FEducation Secretary Gillian Keegan will
OL,11,Fdiscuss the issue with unions, who have
OL,12,Fcalled it "undemocratic".              
OL,14,FIt will be on a voluntary basis at     
OL,15,Ffirst but, in the future, Ms Keegan    
OL,16,Fsaid the government could use powers   
OL,17,Fintroduced earlier this year.          
OL,19,FUnions have said it is an attack on    
OL,20,Fteachers' right to strike.             
